pg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pumpkin-Juice-Recipe-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pumpkin-Juice-Recipe-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pumpkin-Juice-Recipe-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pumpkin-Juice-Recipe-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pumpkin-Juice-Recipe-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pumpkin-Juice-Recipe-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pumpkin-Juice-Recipe-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pumpkin-Juice-Recipe.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-ingredients-in-nbsp-harry-potter-pumpkin-juice-recipe\"\u003eIngredients in Harry Potter Pumpkin Juice Recipe\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eApple Cider\u003c/strong\u003e – Anything you can find in the juice aisle at your local grocery store will work. You can even use apple juice if you can’t locate apple cider. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePumpkin Puree \u003c/strong\u003e– Yes, the same thing you use to make pumpkin pie filling. You may even have a can hiding in your pantry already. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSugar\u003c/strong\u003e – To add a hint of sweetness. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVanilla Extract\u003c/strong\u003e – For some added depth and flavor. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePumpkin Pie Spice\u003c/strong\u003e – A blend of spices that includes cinnamon, nutmeg, cloves and ginger.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis is a \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/4bppfEY\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\"\u003epitcher\u003c/a\u003e recipe. I also used these\u003ca href=\"https://amzn.t